{"tid":1368332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[元朗踢波] 點去水邊村遊樂場","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:03:31.000Z","uid":93208,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"91e005bc29cd60ca4f95a1fbed9334e625c8d384","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"聽日3點想約人踢波，愈多人愈好<br />\n共有2個方法<br />\nA.朗屏西鐵站落方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGfiDNE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGfiDNE.png&h=5bd368b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.B2出口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5hAF14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5hAF14.png&h=7c32d655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RtgqtO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RtgqtO.png&h=c3a0f170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.T字位 轉左一直行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHw9Lye.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHw9Lye.png&h=87d4a875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRgecdg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRgecdg.png&h=832712ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.第二個T字位 轉右落天橋 (轉左就元朗廣場)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZXwYTT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZXwYTT.png&h=dec5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7z4WqyV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7z4WqyV.png&h=f6fbeca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.落天橋過馬路 行左邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XejzceD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXejzceD.png&h=70b639b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBgRes0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBgRes0.png&h=3122aed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5.到紅綠燈位唔洗過馬路 沿路行右手邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHswYVz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHswYVz.png&h=926ec10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdBYDVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdBYDVC.png&h=e2a62fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 10點方向就係水邊村遊樂場 <br />\n過4條馬路就到對面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TiZbYWi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTiZbYWi.png&h=dd808fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nB.元朗西鐵站落方法(少圖)<br />\n1.輕鐵站出口出 落電梯<br />\n會經過元朗連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQJcJpj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQJcJpj.png&h=0e7bb826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.上任何一架輕鐵都得 豐連路站落<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyE3P4S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyE3P4S.png&h=a2ee55fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3.落車行行人路方向(上天橋就元朗廣場)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWioP5J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWioP5J.png&h=c6bf50a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4.過馬路沿右邊行 到紅綠燈過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/buAVGcX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbuAVGcX.png&h=46cd9de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZKzcjD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZKzcjD.png&h=ee830bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5.對面就係水邊村遊樂場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrUvu6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrUvu6F.png&h=71f3d121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水邊村遊樂場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KcMNT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KcMNT5.png&h=9c8cecda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日見啦，我帶波<br />\n你地帶定Pat街啲人好狼死，一定要小心<br />\n幫手推下等多啲人嚟踢波啦"},{"pid":"d94f02c2172a76036e74bca7422e9f2d3f8865e9","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"生於元朗，有種責任"},{"pid":"7991b09537b0e160bb93fb54e391126c86844dc1","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ef5e92e099ef24653de98998f4380b6152c11c1e","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a9850acaf331b809743ea701e2fd00b49ee6ac05","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"07d01cc5a068d2c80951eb884d7bf884d8c35349","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"f8c4c5479ebf701bb49f1acf53ad0fa70a3473ff","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"bbb950cb081bed063b4076c3541bf7a7670671c3","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"唔夠人踢波呀"},{"pid":"b1f01d94a8039e07a1b9922a55df668e68d5a267","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"03d3f9f4bac740e618672f47c528ca3a2d94a049","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"b1d1f4c5e3e48f5e9d32d65706ca7bc7bd4d58a7","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"d0775fca49bef0256836d8c83f16eedc605d08df","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"46d49f476c61c3e39d78a02910e1ef9ce904088c","tid":1368332,"uid":93208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a6ccd58db5f078dd15fc9a46fb1c057ddec4f5d9","tid":1368332,"